snippet.title: Ryan's Rescue Squad | Announce Trailer US
snippet.description:
Are you ready to rescue Ryan's friends from the evil clutches of Dark Titan and his fiendish allies? Play as Ryan and his friends in 4 fascinating worlds and save the day! 

#RyansRescueSquad is coming soon to all platforms! 

Learn more 👉 https://outrightgames.com/games/ryans-rescue-squad/
